Improvement & the Reflective Cycle | Strategise Over-Explained | Ep. 1

This is the first episode of our new series 'Strategise Over-Explained'. This series will contain longer, podcast style, videos on esports related topics where we dive deeper into the topics of main channel videos, or discuss new topics that we have been dying to talk about. 

This episode is about the Reflective Cycle, a system to speed up your improvement through reflection and adaptation. Feel free to ask any questions in the comments and we'll try to answer them as soon as possible!

Check out the main video on this topic below:
